|---|---|---|
| **Sync Algorithm** | Yjs CRDT + OT for formatting | Best of both; industry-proven |
| **Transport** | WebSocket | Bidirectional, low-latency |
| **Conflict Resolution** | Yjs (don't roll your own) | TP2 problem makes custom OT dangerous |
| **Offline** | IndexedDB via Yjs provider | Automatic merge on reconnect |
| **Presence** | Yjs Awareness protocol | Built-in, efficient |
| **Server Role** | Hub + persistence (not resolver) | CRDT resolves conflicts client-side |
| **Document Storage** | MongoDB (snapshots) | Flexible schema, good read perf |
| **Operation Log** | Cassandra | Append-only, time-series optimized |
| **Cache/Pub-Sub** | Redis Cluster | Sub-ms latency, cross-server sync |
| **Search** | Elasticsearch | Full-text, async indexed |
| **Load Balancing** | Consistent hash by doc_id | Serialize ops per document |
| **Security** | JWT + per-op permission checks | Defense in depth |
| **Observability** | Prometheus + OTel + Grafana | Three pillars: metrics/logs/traces |
| **Scaling** | K8s HPA + geo-distribution | Elastic, latency-optimized |

